devdoc.author: Enis Tola
devdoc.details: Tamacoinchi is a smart contract that allows users to raise their own cute virtual pet. Every transaction is written on the Ethereum blockchain. Feed, pet and raise your new best friend. But be careful: if you're pet starves to death, you have to ask a friend to revive it! * Tamacoinchi earns money by offering paid feed() and revive() methods user can use to keep their pets alive or revive them if they die! That's what creatorOfThisContract is used for
